title: Marvel Noir Pack (2008-2010) (75% Digital-HR) (Minutemen+Empire)
description:
OVERVIEW:

    " Marvel Noir is a 2009-2010 Marvel Comics alternative continuity
      combining elements of film noir and pulp fiction with the Marvel
      Universe. The central premise of the mini-series replaces super
      powers with driven, noir-flavored characterization. " 

     -- <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvel_Noir" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvel_Noir</a>

CONTAINS:

   Highest-available-quality releases for each of the participating titles,
   including "Deadpool Pulp", which may or may not officially belong here.

      Marvel Noir                           (2008)                 (Kingpin)
      Spider-Man Noir                       (2009) (Dgtl''300)     (Minutemen)
      Spider-Man Noir - Eyes Without a Face (2010)                 (Minutemen-DTs)
      X-Men Noir                            (2009)                 (Minutemen-Locke)
      X-Men Noir - Mark of Cain             (2010)                 (Minutemen-DTs)
      Daredevil Noir                        (2009) (Dgtl-1920)     (G85-Empire)
      Wolverine Noir                        (2009) (Dgtl-TPB-1920) (G85-Empire)
      Punisher Noir                         (2009) (Dgtl-1920)     (G85-Empire)
      Luke Cage Noir                        (2009) (Dgtl-1920)     (G85-Empire)
      Iron Man Noir                         (2010) (Dgtl-1920)     (G85-Empire)
      Weapon X Noir                         (2010)                 (Minutemen-DTs)
      Deadpool Pulp                         (2010) (Dgtl''300)     (Minutemen-PhD)
